<h2>{{mentorName}} Accepted Your Mentorship Request!</h2>

<p>Hello {{menteeName}},</p>

<p>Wonderful news!
  {{mentorName}}
  has accepted your mentorship request. You now have an active mentor!</p>

<div class='info-box'>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 10px 0;'><strong>Your Mentor:</strong>
    {{mentorName}}</p>
  {{#if responseMessage}}
    <p style='margin: 10px 0 0 0;'><strong>Message from
        {{mentorName}}:</strong></p>
    <p
      style='margin: 5px 0 0 0; padding: 10px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-left: 3px solid #3A5A40; font-style: italic;'
    >
      "{{responseMessage}}"
    </p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a href='spiriment://chat' class='button'>Message Your Mentor</a>
</p>

<p style='margin-top: 20px;'>
  <strong>What You Can Do Now:</strong><br />
  • Message
  {{mentorName}}
  directly through the app<br />
  • Schedule your first mentoring session<br />
  • Share your spiritual goals and areas where you'd like guidance<br />
  • Ask questions about your faith journey
</p>

<p>We're excited to see your spiritual growth through this mentorship. Remember
  to be open, ask questions, and actively participate in your sessions.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  <strong>Tips for a Successful Mentorship:</strong><br />
  • Be consistent with scheduled sessions<br />
  • Come prepared with questions or topics to discuss<br />
  • Be open and honest about your spiritual journey<br />
  • Apply what you learn and share your progress<br />
  • Respect your mentor's time and expertise
</p>

<p>May this mentorship bring you closer to God and help you grow in your faith.</p>

<p style='margin-top: 30px;'>
  Blessings,<br />
  <strong style='color: #3A5A40;'>The Spiriment Team</strong>
</p>